118
00:05:16,983 --> 00:05:19,152
You wanted him under
an exclusive contract

119
00:05:19,194 --> 00:05:20,862
with your hospital.

120
00:05:20,904 --> 00:05:23,490
Someone like Duntsch, from
a program like Semmes-Murphey,

121
00:05:23,531 --> 00:05:24,491
he's the perfect target.

122
00:05:24,532 --> 00:05:26,117
Not only is he marketable,

123
00:05:26,159 --> 00:05:28,995
