You look at someone like me,

187
00:09:24,439 --> 00:09:28,568
someone younger, smarter,

188
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:31,446
more capable,

189
00:09:31,488 --> 00:09:34,407
just filling up all the spaces,

190
00:09:34,449 --> 00:09:37,369
